dct_description_sm: Printed at Base Printing Plant 29th Engineers, U.S. Army 1918.
Relief shown by contours, spot heights, and hachuring.
Shows railways, roads (including unfinished), fortress, buildings, waterways, various locations (Y.M.C.A. facilities, post offices, telegraph offices, cemeteries, churches, etc.), vegetation.
dct_creator_sm: United States, Army., Corps of Engineers.
